// To compile this file use this command:
$ arm-linux-gnueabihf-gcc serial-loopback-test.c -o serial-loopback-test 

How to use this application:

Use a link to connect these pins:
J31.3 with J31.5

The program is testing the chosen serial port with string or file by  TX-RX loopback.

// To run this program use this command
$ ./serial-loopback-test /dev/ttymxc1 115200 "fedevel"
